DELICATESKIN

Sheep oil moisturizes and penetrates the skin  
Extracts components from wool that are compatible with the skin  

Fine small molecules penetrate the skin  
Moisturizing skin, gentle and skin-friendly  

What is sheep oil?  

Sheep oil refers to lanolin. It is similar in composition to the protective layer of the skin, providing protection for the skin, moisturizing it, hydrating dry skin, and increasing skin hydration.
src: 绵羊油水润 沁透肌肤
萃取羊毛中贴合肌肤成分
细小分子 沁透肌肤
绵羊油是指羊毛脂，于肌肤保护层成分相似，能为肌肤提供保护，水润肌肤，湿润干燥肌肤，提升肌肤水分。
